Avar Download Manager Config

Usage:
  avar config set <name> <value>
  avar config get <name> [--defaultValue=<defaultValue>]
  avar config reset <name>
  avar config reset-all
  avar config save <path>
  avar config load <path>
  avar config --help

Options:
  -h --help     Show help for config command.
